# 🖼️ Image with Link

A simple HTML project demonstrating how to wrap an image inside a clickable link — one of my early hands-on projects while learning HTML.

🔗 **Live Demo:** [sprightly-pie-5cf9a5.netlify.app](https://sprightly-pie-5cf9a5.netlify.app)

---

## 📌 About

This project practices two core HTML concepts:
- Embedding images using the `<img>` tag
- Wrapping elements in anchor `<a>` tags to make them clickable links

